      • hashCode

        public int hashCode()

        This hashCode implementation is specific for JPA entities and uses a fixed int value to be able to identify the entity in collections after a new id is assigned to the entity, following the article in https://vladmihalcea.com/2016/06/06/how-to-implement-equals-and-hashcode-using-the-jpa-entity-identifier/
